# The JSON looks similar to: {"symbol":"BTCUSDT","price":"63000.00000000"}
# Use `grep`, `sed`, `awk`, or `jq` (if installed) to extract just the exact price number.
# Print the output in this format: "Current price of $COIN is: $X.XX"

